d\">default</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">BackgroundLetterAvatars</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Stack direction<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"row\"</span> spacing<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Avatar <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token function\">stringAvatar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Guide Hub\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"#673ABE\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Avatar <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token function\">stringAvatar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Infinit Bility\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"#377BCD\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Avatar <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token function\">stringAvatar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>